Category:Unidentified Sith of the One Sith

nodes.text: This Human Sith was one of five members of the One Sith who ambushed a group of Jedi on Daluuj in 137 ABY. He killed a Human female Jedi before being struck down by Wolf Sazen and Shado Vao.
